      <h1 class="h4 mb-3">20. Render repeated component instances with <code>het-for</code></h1>
      <div class="tutorial-content mb-4">
        <p><code>het-for</code> uses the same structural-template rules as <code>het-if</code>, but the source signal must hold a <code>Map</code>. Each Map key is the clone key, and each Map value must have signal properties.</p>
        <p>Each Map entry is keyed by its string or number key, and the entry value's signal properties are forwarded into the cloned component root, so every <code>todoItem</code> receives its own <code>label</code> signal.</p>
        <p>The source signal is still just a signal. To add an item, assign a new Map:</p>
        <p>Reference documentation:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="reference/components#het-for"><code>het-for</code></a></li>
          <li><a href="reference/components#structural-templates">Structural templates</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <form method="post" action="/preview" target="tutorial-preview" data-tutorial-form>
        <input type="hidden" name="html" data-editor-output="html">
        <input type="hidden" name="js" data-editor-output="js">
        <input type="hidden" name="css" data-editor-output="css">

        <div class="mb-3">
          <label class="form-label fw-semibold" for="html-source">HTML</label>
          <textarea id="html-source" class="d-none" data-editor="html">&lt;section het-component="todoList"&gt;
  &lt;label&gt;
    New todo
    &lt;input type="text" value="Ship it" het-model="newLabel"&gt;
  &lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;button type="button" het-on="click-&gt;addTodo"&gt;Add todo&lt;/button&gt;

  &lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;template het-for="items"&gt;
      &lt;li het-component="todoItem"&gt;
        &lt;span het-text="label"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/template&gt;
  &lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;</textarea>
          <div class="editor-host" data-editor-host="html"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-3">
          <label class="form-label fw-semibold" for="js-source">JavaScript</label>
          <textarea id="js-source" class="d-none" data-editor="js">let nextTodoId = 1;

function todo(label) {
  return {
    label: HET.signals.signal(label),
  };
}

HET.registerComponent('todoList', ({ signals }) => {
  signals.items = HET.signals.signal(new Map([
    [nextTodoId++, todo('Write HTML')],
    [nextTodoId++, todo('Enhance behavior')],
  ]));

  return {
    addTodo() {
      const label = signals.newLabel.value.trim();

      if (!label) return;

      signals.items.value = new Map([
        ...signals.items.value,
        [nextTodoId++, todo(label)],
      ]);
      signals.newLabel.value = '';
    },
  };
});

HET.registerComponent('todoItem');
HET.init();</textarea>
          <div class="editor-host" data-editor-host="js"></div>
